Package: berryFunctions
Type: Package
Title: Function Collection Related to Plotting and Hydrology
Version: 1.9.23
Date: 2016-03-31
Imports:
    graphics,
    stats
Suggests:
    RColorBrewer,
    pbapply
Author: Berry Boessenkool
Maintainer: Berry Boessenkool <berry-b@gmx.de>
Description: Draw horizontal histograms, color scatterpoints by 3rd dimension,
    enhance date- and log-axis plots, zoom in X11 graphics, use the unit
    hydrograph in a linear storage cascade, convert lists to data.frames, fit
    multiple functions by regression (power, reciprocal, exponential, logarithmic,
    polynomial, rational).
License: GPL-2
URL: https://github.com/brry/berryFunctions
RoxygenNote: 5.0.1
